<rss xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" version="2.0"><channel><lastBuildDate>Fri, 06 Aug 2021 22:27:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><item><category>法國</category><title>花絮:史上首位奧運空手道冠軍是法國巴黎地鐵員工</title><link>https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B/20210806-%E8%8A%B1%E7%B5%AE-%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E9%A6%96%E4%BD%8D%E5%A5%A7%E9%81%8B%E7%A9%BA%E6%89%8B%E9%81%93%E5%86%A0%E8%BB%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E5%9C%B0%E9%90%B5%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5</link><description>
